Detailed Description

Public class representing a JavaScript console message from WebCore.

This could be a issued by a call to one of the console logging functions (e.g. console.log('...')) or a JavaScript error on the page. To receive notifications of these messages, override the WebChromeClient#onConsoleMessage(ConsoleMessage) function.
